##Diary of the outbreak | day twelve of the siege of Wuhan

Plantifulsoul

Introduction to behindmylife

2020.2.3

If I hadn't kept my diary, it's hard to believe that 12 days after the city was closed, many places started to work one after another. My classmate worked in a securities company. After the market opened, he worked from home, and confessed that his mind was not fully adapted to the rhythm of the resumption of work, "It's like a lifetime ago when you turn on your company computer and watch the market YTHT. " . Our unit will start work next week, the current holiday, although I can not say before the end of the month can not go back, the new document requires Hubei staff not to rush to work, first isolation at home 5-7 days.

Joking with her classmates, "now the family relationship is extremely harmonious. Everyone keeps their heads down on their mobile phones. They don't talk much. They don't dare to quarrel casually. After the quarrel, they have no place to go. They have to stay at home and stare at each other. " She said that you still talk at least, several people in her family, except for dinner, are not in a room, her mother closed the door after work "reduce contact with the family" , his father's living room watching TV brush cell phone, she in the room open projection game watching variety show, very conscious of the division, to avoid gathering.

Today downstairs, the community has been hanging on the door of the "zero infection" red signs, particularly eye-catching, turn around, we are several temporary "zero infection" signs. Yesterday saw the next building wearing protective clothing staff sprayed disinfectant, do not know if there are suspected patients, now the situation is more serious, more and more families gathered infection, one sick, the whole family, highly infectious.

After more than 10 days of closed management, I felt a little nervous and panic. At night, I sat on my back and felt cool. I asked if I had developed chills after the incubation period. Wechat spent 49 yuan for an online consultation, the doctor replied, "please do not panic, sometimes psychological and emotional will also lead to physical conditions, " a little laugh or cry, to hope that I was just a false alarm.

Buy The cat food hospital has signed for, every day with their little video cloud suction cat, more and more want him. The doctor said that his belly had shrunk, he didn't move much in the cage, his appetite dropped, I didn't prepare any meat jerky and other snacks for him, he was obviously thin to the naked eye, alas, I like fat cats best, and I am eager to fatten them up, the Meaty Blob, especially the soft belly, feels comfortable, and now back before liberation, the plan has temporarily failed. Yesterday, someone abandoned Siam on Weibo, the snow on the roof of the coal mine, and the snowflakes hanging from his beard. The video shows him looking haggard.

There have been several reports of small and medium-sized enterprises struggling to survive recently: farmers burying chickens and ducks alive, flower shop owners smashing flowers, fruits and vegetables can not be shipped out to rot in the ground... I asked on wechat whether the strawberry seller Wuhan Tongcheng can deliver goods, their strawberry fields are in Jiangxia District, the fruits are big and sweet, they can be received on the same day as normal delivery, they tell the shop that SF express hasn't stopped yet, they can have the price raised by express delivery, I buy several boxes of strawberry support (and it is delicious) .

Store Reply Very Helpless, they asked SF Express, very period do not answer, the fastest also have to wait for the second half of February. Wuhan slowly warm, do not pick on time can only watch the strawberry rotten in the field, the whole family eat strawberries every day, a basin to eat, fortunately there are children at home, like to eat strawberries, adults had "see strawberry color change. ". They also said that they donated several truckloads of fresh strawberries to a nearby hospital, which is at least a good deed. If they could sell them normally, who would be willing to make the effort to give them away for free, "where is to send strawberries, is a car of money, the original hope to visit relatives and friends in the New Year business can get up, the results did not get, but also lost a lot of money. ".

Ask another strawberry grocer in Daliang Mountains, Daliang Mountains's small, sweet and sour strawberries. Shop Owners said their business was also affected, the village during the New Year not allowed to go out, no strawberry garden care, even if picked can not sell, their village few like to eat, all point to orders from outside the province. But these days slowly recovery, logistics began to take orders, wechat has several customers ordered strawberry, "this batch of strawberry hair began to sell loquat, are boutique fruit, and so you can look for me to buy. ".

I Buy Cat food shop in Shenzhen, cat canned, cat litter store in Wuhan, Wuhan Fa Xian Express, the next day can be delivered. The pet store in Wuhan has already typed out a notice on its front page, "unable to ship, recovery time uncertain, I am very sorry. " Wechat asked if they could send it from the same city, and also replied, I can't, the warehouse is across the river, and Wuchang can't send it. After the closure of the city of Wuhan, their business was greatly affected, orders could not be delivered, many customers who could not wait for them cancelled their refunds, and the purchase of goods in the warehouse was also suspended. Now they can only take out a portion to donate to volunteers or animal protection organizations in the same city, to help cats that are about to run out of food.

Every day I see couples sitting on the doorstep of a roadside Lanzhou noodle shop, twirling their kitchen hats with their fingers, doing nothing. They usually stay at the hotel. In fact, they have stocks ready before the festival. Flour and beef are enough for a month or two, but no one eats them at all. The boilers are burnt to a crisp. Normally, they "keep the business going" by relying on the residents nearby and the customers who work in the furniture city, now there is no list, the couple can only play in front of the mobile phone every day, "but no one is good, we are not enough masks, now a shop closed can save masks, if someone really eat noodles, we have to do health disinfection mask. ".

I finally found the eyebrow shaver in a Rawson convenience store, and my eyebrows were saved. In addition to the hot processed food, everything on the shelves is quite complete, including cakes, bread, instant noodles, Ham and sausages, as well as basic household items. There are also instant pasta, spicy crayfish, Milk Tea Jelly and spicy fried rice cakes in the freezer, i suddenly crave the taste of Kimchi and Korean hot sauce, especially the hot sauce on the top of the Stone Pot Bibimbap. There are two cans of Kimchi in the refrigerator in Xi'an.

I asked the shop assistant how they were so well supplied, and the shop assistant told me that they were always supplied by Zhongbai Logistics, and that they had daily car deliveries, but were short of fresh food, such as steamed buns, Guandong, boiled tea, eggs, and so on, plus, it's right next to the office building, so no one's working right now, and there's not a lot of people going out there to buy anything, except maybe a couple of take-out orders. I also wonder if they have subsidies to work during extraordinary times, after all, the manpower is also small, unlike the usual number of people can shift, brother smiled a few, turned to continue inventory, "a salary is good, what do you think. ".

My father went shopping on his bicycle and ran to two big supermarkets which were closed. I was puzzled to hear that we had informed the big supermarkets that they were open all the time. My father said that because some of the employees had contracted pneumonia, they were put under quarantine and the supermarkets were also closed. My classmate's community property has been linked to the nearby food delivery shops, which take the community as a unit, place orders online or in wechat groups, vegetables, fruits and eggs can be bought, delivered every day at 4:00 pm, and the residents register their names at the gate of the community, to a certain extent, also "encourage everyone not to go out, " the box Ma Qun also began to have a community to buy food, we here have not informed the property, intend to ask tomorrow, can facilitate the residents, collective delivery orders.

Weibo saw the secretary of the screen shot at the door, got pneumonia, the community does not care, the hospital does not accept, for fear of infecting the family, in despair jumped under the overpass. The entrance of the secretary's Office is relatively close to my home. When I was a child, I often went there to play, so when I saw this news, my mood was complicated. There were comments saying, "who lives near, can you put a bunch of white chrysanthemums under the bridge? " And then I replied, "where can I buy chrysanthemums? The flower shop is all closed. " It's making me feel worse.

"The moment we are born, it is as if we have made a pact for a lifetime, but perhaps one day we will ask ourselves who signed it for me... everyone has their own pain, but everyone is equally sad... May I fall with the bubble, never to the ground, clean, pure, naked. "

The day before yesterday, the diary was harmonious part, turned into a picture can not be sent out, I hand, the national trend to return to work, the work of all went to work... content in front of the same treatment, regardless of large and small, all "can not see. ".
